<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Acquired digital fibrokeratoma.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows polypoid skin lesion with variably hyperplastic epidermis and is composed of dense collagen fibers oriented predominantly in vertical direction.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
