  </note>
  <note>
    <title>Actinic keratosis [SKIAK]</title>
    <created>20170728T063004Z</created>
    <updated>20250310T023440Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><br/></div><div>DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>Actinic keratosis, __, excisional biopsy</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>GROSS DESCRIPTION:</div><div>The specimen is composed of ___ piece_ of ___ tissue, measuring __ x ___ x ___ cm.</div><div><br/></div><div>All are embedded in ___ cassette.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Actinic keratosis.</div><div><br/></div><div>MICROSCOPIC DESCRIPTION:</div><div>Section shows skin tissue revealing parakeratosis and hyperkeratosis of squamous</div><div>epithelium, with atypia predominantly affecting the basal layer. The epidermis is</div><div>focally proliferating in budlike downgrowths into the papillary dermis. Solar</div><div>elastosis and chronic inflammatory infiltrate are seen in the dermis.</div><div><br/></div><div> 性質: 0 benign</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
