<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Acute inflammation with fungal infection.<br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows skin tissue with focal intraepithelial neutrophilic infiltrate, and fungal spores and hyphae within the keratin layer.</div></en-note>      ]]>
