<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Angioleiomyoma</span></span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Microscopic description:</span></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Section shows one well-defined nodular lesion composed of proliferative muscle bundles and compressed vessels.</span></span></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
