<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Arteriovenous hemangioma.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows skin tissue with intradermal proliferation of numerous thick-walled vessels lined with plump endothelial cells.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
