    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>The lesion is characterized by markedly thickened keratin layer and hyperplastic epithelium.</div></en-note>      ]]>
