    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">PATHOLOGIC DIAGNOSIS:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Skin, ___, excision --- </span><span style="line-height: 1.45;">Epidermoid cyst.</span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Gross description:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">The specimen consists of _ pieces of grayish tissue measuring up to ___ cm.</span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">All for section.</span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Microscopic description:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">The dermally-located cyst is lined by stratified squamous epithelium and its lumen contains laminated keratin fragments.</span></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
