<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Epidermoid cyst.</div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Microscopic description:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">The dermally-located cyst is lined by stratified squamous epithelium and its lumen contains laminated keratin fragments.</span></div></en-note>      ]]>
